      "title": "Numbered Discourses 4 ",
      "expandable": false
    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:1.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:2.1",
          "pli": "“Catūhi kho, gahapati, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Householder, when a noble disciple does four things they are practicing appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:2.2",
          "pli": "Katamehi catūhi? ",
          "en": "What four? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:2.3",
          "pli": "Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti cīvarena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti piṇḍapātena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti senāsanena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena. ",
          "en": "It’s when a noble disciple serves the mendicant Saṅgha with robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:2.4",
          "pli": "Imehi kho, gahapati, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikanti. ",
          "en": "When a noble disciple does these four things they are practicing appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:3.1",
          "pli": "Gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ, ",
          "en": "Those who are astute practice the way "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:3.2",
          "pli": "paṭipajjanti paṇḍitā; ",
          "en": "that’s appropriate for laypeople. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:3.3",
          "pli": "Sammaggate sīlavante, ",
          "en": "They provide those who are ethical "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:3.4",
          "pli": "cīvarena upaṭṭhitā. ",
          "en": "and on the right path with robes, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.1",
          "pli": "Piṇḍapātasayanena, ",
          "en": "alms-food, lodgings, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.2",
          "pli": "Gilānappaccayena ca; ",
          "en": "and supplies for the sick. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.3",
          "pli": "Tesaṃ divā ca ratto ca, ",
          "en": "Their merit always grows "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.4",
          "pli": "Sadā puññaṃ pavaḍḍhati; ",
          "en": "by day and by night. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.5",
          "pli": "Saggañca kamatiṭṭhānaṃ, ",
          "en": "They pass on to a place in heaven, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.6",
          "pli": "Kammaṃ katvāna bhaddakan”ti. ",
          "en": "having done excellent deeds.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.7",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:4.8",
          "pli": "Puññābhisandavaggo paṭhamo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:5.1",
          "pli": "Dve puññābhisandā dve ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:5.2",
          "pli": "saṃvāsā samajīvino; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:5.3",
          "pli": "Suppavāsā sudatto ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.60:5.4",
          "pli": "bhojanaṃ gihisāmicīti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
